Text: Great first show, looking forward to more to come. TY TvTeam!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

But yeah dude, you should label this as Season 1 Episode 1, I think they're disregarding the internet series for now, and making this their new series. Season 2 ended on a cliffhanger, and this one barely touched it. But whatever, doesn't matter; just in case you were wondering.
